{
  "texts": [
    "Bostrom defines Narrow AI as \"the application of optimised algorithms in the service of solving a narrow task\" (Bostrom 2014).",
    "That said, in our specific case study, the commercial and the political can be hard to disentangle.",
    "Privacy risks arise from the merging of publicly available data and private commercial data.",
    "Pollsters are commercial enterprises providing a public good; accurate pre-election polling translates into enhanced reputation within the marketresearch industry, which incentivises private sector companies to request their services.",
    "Accurate predictions are highly profitable."
  ]
}